**DPI:** The DeFi Pulse Index DPI enables non-technical investors to access the same returns as highly technical crypto insiders. DPI was formed as a partnership between leading crypto teams TokenSet and DeFi Pulse.

**DPI Value:** There is no impermanent loss because DPI holds the underlying assets directly and is rebalanced monthly, according to the methodology. We don't use liquidity pools for portfolio construction, ensuring that investors are not exposed to impermanent loss.




